:true,"entry_ids":["n6723","n6728"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8E%D9%88%D9%8E%D9%91%D9%81%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"hollow, cavity, depression"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"interior, inner","examples":[{"text":"فاغرة (var. فاكرة).\nالماهية: حب يشبه الحمص له حب كالمحلب وفي جوفه حب أسود كالشهدانج يحمل من السفالة.\nالطبع: حارة يابسة في الثالثة.\nالخواص: فيها تحليل وقبض.\nأعضاء الغذاء: يدخل في الأدوية المصلحة للمعدة والكبد الباردتين وينفع من سوء الاستمراء البارد.\nأعضاء النفض: ينفع من الإسهال البارد ويعقل البطن.","english":"Sichuan pepper:\nIts essence: The fruit resembles chickpeas, it has fruits like mahaleb cherry, and in its inner there is a black fruit like hempseed, born from below.\nIts nature: Hot and dry in the third degree.\nIts peculiarities: In it there is discharging and constipation.\nAlimentary organs: It is put into drugs by reason of availing the stomach and the liver when they are cold and it is useful against calamities of cold appetite.\nExcretory organs: It helps against cold diarrhoea and constricts the belly."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"belly, abdomen"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"north","tags":["al-Andalus"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of جَافَ (jāfa, “to be hollow; to reach the interior of”) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to hollow out"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be hollow, to be concave"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of جَوِفَ (jawifa) (form I); hollowness"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of جَوِفَ (jawifa) (form I); amplitude"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"masculine plural of أَجْوَف (ʔajwaf)","tags":["form-of","masculine","plural"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root ج و ف (j w f). The sense “inner” suggests a relation with Egyptian jwf (“flesh”) since the flesh is in the “inner” part of the body. Compare Hebrew גוף (guf, “body”)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6723","headword_ar":"جَوَفٌ","root":"jwf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hollow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wide and hollow within:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(PS:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being empty, vacant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"void:"},{"kind":"text","text":"an inf. n. of which the verb is of the class of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEiba","text_ar":"تَعِبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAfa","text_ar":"جَافَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawifa","text_ar":"جَوِفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAfa","text_ar":"خَافَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", sec. pers."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jifota","text_ar":"جِفْتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yajaAfu","text_ar":"يَجَافُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Msb:) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being wide, spacious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ample:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) the inf. n., or source, whence"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aYo'N A^ajowafu","text_ar":"شَىْءٌ اَجْوَفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) [See also 10.]       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAfahu","text_ar":"جَافَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yajuwfu","text_ar":"يَجُوفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawofN","text_ar":"جَوْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It reached his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawof","text_ar":"جَوْف"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inside,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"interior,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (TA.)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(medicine)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"entered his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawof","text_ar":"جَوْف"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA. [See also 8.]) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAfatohu AljiraAHapu","text_ar":"جَافَتْهُ الجِرَاحَةُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The wound reached his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawof","text_ar":"جَوْف"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaEanahu fajaAfahu","text_ar":"طَعَنَهُ فَجَافَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AjAfhu","text_ar":"اجافهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He pierced him and pierced his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawof","text_ar":"جَوْف"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh, Msb:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jw~fhu","text_ar":"جوّفهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tajowiyfN","text_ar":"تَجْوِيفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he pierced him in his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawof","text_ar":"جَوْف"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jufotuhu biAlT~aEonapi","text_ar":"جُفْتُهُ بِالطَّعْنَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~aEonapa","text_ar":"الطَّعْنَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajafotuhu","text_ar":"اَجَفْتُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I made the spear-wound,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like, to reach his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawof","text_ar":"جَوْف"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Ks, A 'Obeyd, S, K.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAfa AlS~ayoda","text_ar":"جَافَ الصَّيْدَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made the arrow to enter the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawof","text_ar":"جَوْف"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the object of the chase."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["PS","Msb","K","Mgh"]},{"entry_id":"n6728","headword_ar":"جَوْفٌ","root":"jwf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A hollow; an interior empty, vacant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"void, space;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a vacancy:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajowaAfN","text_ar":"اَجْوَافٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": this is the primary signification: then it was used in relation to a thing capable of being occupied and of being unoccupied; so as to be applied in the sense next following. (Msb.) ―         -b2-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inside,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"interior,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, KL,) of a house [&c.]. (Msb.) ―         -b3-  [The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"midst,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"middle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing.] ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A low,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"depressed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and wide,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tract,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion, of land,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ground:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is wider than the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iEob","text_ar":"شِعْب"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"water-courses termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tilaAE","text_ar":"تِلَاع"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the valleys, flow into it; and it has"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jirafap","text_ar":"جِرَفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abrupt, water-worn, banks"},{"kind":"text","text":"]:"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sometimes it is wider than a valley, and deeper:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sometimes it is a plain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soft, tract, that retains water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sometimes it is completely round, so that it retains water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to IAar, it signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a valley:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, as some say, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"interior"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baTon","text_ar":"بَطْن"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a valley."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b5-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"belly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abdomen,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a man: (S, K:) or, accord. to ISd, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"interior of the belly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part upon which close the shoulder-blades and the upper arms and the ribs and the two flanks"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlS~uqolaAni","text_ar":"الصُّقْلَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"): (TA:) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chest,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thorax;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e., the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part of the body that is separated from the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baTon","text_ar":"بَطْن"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"belly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abdomen,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HijaAb","text_ar":"حِجَاب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"diaphragm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"midriff"},{"kind":"text","text":"];"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"containing the heart and its appertenances:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj in his “ Khalk el-Insán: ”) pl. as above. (TA.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAy^ifN","text_ar":"جَايِفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". It is one of the words that are not used adverbially except with prepositions. (Sb, TA.) It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA tanosawuA Aljawofa","text_ar":"لَا تَنْسَوُا الجَوْفَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wamaA waEaY","text_ar":"وَمَا وَعَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Forget not ye the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jwf","text_ar":"جوف"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and what it hath collected"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; meaning what enters into it, of food and beverage: but some say that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aljwf","text_ar":"الجوف"},{"kind":"text","text":"here means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the belly and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faroj","text_ar":"فَرْج"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vulva,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pudendum muliebre"},{"kind":"text","text":"], together, which are also called ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^ajowafaAni","text_ar":"الاَجْوَفَانِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": and some say that the meaning is,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the heart and what it hath retained, and kept in memory,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the knowledge of God. (A 'Obeyd, TA.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^ajowaAfu","text_ar":"الاَجْوَافُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also applied by the people of El-Ghowr (K) and of El-Yemen (TA) to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The tents"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fasaATiyT","text_ar":"فَسَاطِيط"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of their"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eum~aAl","text_ar":"عُمَّال"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"governors,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"collectors of the poor-rates"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawofu All~ayoli","text_ar":"جَوْفُ اللَّيْلِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA=xiru","text_ar":"الا=خِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", occurring in a trad., means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The last third of the night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the fifth of the sixths of the night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) not the half, as some assert. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","KL","S","K","TA"]}]}}